        "setup": "Mint a short-lived bearer token for API2 or MCP in a trusted environment. The docs show you can create one with the CLI: `npx -y @transloadit/node auth token --aud mcp`, or via `POST /token`, or the Node SDK helper `mintBearerToken({ aud: 'mcp' })`. Tokens are valid for 6 hours and are meant to be handed to your agent runtime or client.",
